/* Hitme's Note: 
   - Instead of edit character data for every students, using Template + Local Tokens would be a more effiecent method.
   - Documents: https://github.com/Pathoschild/StardewMods/blob/develop/ContentPatcher/docs/author-guide/tokens.md#local-tokens
   - Local tokens is currently in beta, and they don't accept boolean value (from what I remembered), so don't use it unless it's neccessary.
   - NPC data is duplicatable, however the schedule data is not, so if you want to add more student in the future, make sure to edit their schedule as well. 
   - This only work with NPC that exactly the same, if one NPC has special variable, edit  them specifically in this file.
   - When we are done with all sprites + portraits (default + winter), move the rest the code in StudentLoadData.json to the template
   */
